  "texts": [
    "It is evident from the data that human reviewers outperform Mistral LLM in all aspects concerning attention to detail, with particularly significant gaps in nuanced critique and error identification.",
    "This discrepancy underscores the essential role of human intuition and experience in dissecting complex scientific texts, a trait currently underdeveloped in LLMs.",
    "Enhancing the LLM's capabilities in these areas would not only improve the quality of automated reviews but also extend the model's applicability to more critical and complex analytical tasks.",
    "Addressing these gaps through further training and model refinement could en- Review Time Number of Papers 0 20 40 60 80 100 17 50 100 50 Time (Hours) Mistral LLM Human Reviewers Figure 3: Comparative analysis of efficiency and scalability between Mistral LLM and human reviewersable LLMs to provide more valuable insights and support to researchers in the review process.",
    "Efficiency and ScalabilityThe efficiency and scalability of conducting literature reviews with Mistral LLM presented a significant advantage over traditional human review processes."
  ]
